{"text_id":184627,"tokens":["Our"," work"," explores"," the"," connection"," between"," strings"," and"," sigma"," models",","," focusing"," on"," the"," tension","less"," limit","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," limitations"," of"," conventional"," sigma"," models"," in"," capturing"," non","-","polynomial"," interactions",","," we"," investigate"," how"," string"," theory"," provides"," a"," framework"," for"," addressing"," these"," shortcomings","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," in"," the"," tension","less"," limit",","," certain"," string"," modes"," decou","ple"," from"," the"," gravit","on"," and"," can"," be"," identified"," as"," higher","-","derivative"," operators"," of"," the"," sigma"," field","."," This"," discovery"," enables"," us"," to"," apply"," string"," theory"," to"," model"," various"," phenomena"," intractable"," to"," conventional"," field"," theory",","," such"," as"," non","-","perturb","ative"," interactions"," and"," non","-","commutative"," geometries","."," Our"," findings"," suggest"," that"," string"," theory"," offers"," a"," new"," perspective"," on"," understanding"," the"," dynamics"," of"," quantum"," fields"," and"," their"," interactions"," in"," curved"," spacetime","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}